05:32.990 --> 05:38.330
I mean granted my drawing isn't perfect just not completely aligned but if I can get the bottom of the

05:38.330 --> 05:44.920
nose and maybe the mouth lined up like this as well as the bottom of the eyes.

05:45.260 --> 05:46.990
I think that might be good.

05:47.360 --> 05:54.680
Now the ear isn't lined up and that's OK I'm not too worried about that but it's the nose in the eyes

05:54.830 --> 05:56.790
that I'm concerned with here.

05:57.050 --> 06:03.320
So now that I've got that lined up I'm going to press shift to constrain it and then click and drag

06:03.320 --> 06:06.030
it back over here like that.

06:06.170 --> 06:09.150
So it's more in the center of the image.

06:09.200 --> 06:16.890
And now to zoom back out I'm going to press shift commander control J to zoom out to full screen there.

06:17.270 --> 06:20.780
I'll bring the opacity back up to 100 percent.

06:20.780 --> 06:22.360
